  "title": "Personal Care Officer [Buangkok | 5 days | up to $3300] - LCYL",
  "description": "<h3><strong>Personal Care Officer</strong></h3><ul><li><strong>Salary : $2,500 - $3,300</strong></li><li><strong>Location: Buangkok</strong></li><li><strong>Working hours: 5 days - 44 hours / week </strong></li><li><strong>Rotating shift : 8:30am - 6:30pm / 8am - 8pm (AM) / 8pm - 8am  (PM)</strong></li></ul><p><strong>Job Responsibilities</strong></p><ul><li>Plan and supervise the care of residents</li><li>Develop and implement programmes and activities for the well-being of residents</li><li>Put up monthly interview records for residents</li><li>Ensure proper maintenance of the Home's equipment</li><li>Ensure the cleanliness of the Home premises</li></ul><p><strong>Job Requirements</strong></p><ul><li>Diploma in psychology , social work , counselling or relevant field</li><li>Willing to work rotating shifts including night shift and weekends</li><li>Training provided</li></ul><p><br />Cheong Yeat Long | R25145358</p><p>The Supreme HR Advisory Pte Ltd | EA 14C7279</p>",
